--- !u!114 &3174599173851560821
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 8287498470672042513}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2c58c290b7d673d189b082e1d2ef9726, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TalkingHat
  familyQuotes:
  - quotes:
    - quote: ugh
      type: 0
    - quote: Kids! Stop playing now!
      type: 1
    - quote: '*barfs*'
      type: 2
    - quote: I hate all theses crawling creatures!
      type: 3
    - quote: Watch out, a fungus!
      type: 3
    - quote: Did you know the neigbouhrs eat burned toast? They're probably gonna
        get cancer!
      type: 3
    - quote: '*huh*'
      type: 3
    - quote: It looks rotten, don't eat it!
      type: 3
    - quote: Without grandma the house would look like a junkyard.
      type: 3
    - quote: Without grandma the house would look like a junkyard.
      type: 3
    - quote: The only light Maxi enjoys is the one from screens.
      type: 3
    - quote: The only light Maxi enjoys is the one from screens.
      type: 3
    - quote: I hope puberty won't change anything between Maxi and Pina
      type: 3
    - quote: Ah! Max stop creeping up on me!
      type: 3
    human: {fileID: 5816517993243776774}
  - quotes:
    - quote: '*snores*'
      type: 0
    - quote: This ain't real...
      type: 1
    - quote: NOPE *runs away*
      type: 2
    - quote: You call it family, I call it psych ward.
      type: 3
    - quote: The only thing my husband fears is me....and everything else nature
        has to offer.
      type: 3
    - quote: Pina, stop eating the curtains!
      type: 3
    - quote: I'm so glad my mum  lives with us. I'm really a train-wreck of a mother...
      type: 3
    - quote: I can't go to the basement...its for...uh...losers.
      type: 3
    - quote: I'll leave the light on honey.
      type: 3
    - quote: Without grandma the house would look like a junkyard.
      type: 3
    - quote: ' I''m so glad my mum  lives with us. I''m really a train-wreck of a
        mother...'
      type: 3
    - quote: Next summer I'll go camping in australia with Pina and leave mom and
        the boys at fancy hotel.
      type: 3
    - quote: As a child I wasn't allowed to dress up as a clown, guess what I made
        for Pina last halloween...
      type: 3
    - quote: '*ugh* Bernhard you don''t have to wash your shirt after wearing it
        once!'
      type: 3
    human: {fileID: 1035538039935100861}
  - quotes:
    - quote: '*ugh*...just kill me already'
      type: 0
    - quote: '...um...hello? '
      type: 1
    - quote: Please, I don't wanna die! I just say it for attention!
      type: 2
    - quote: Pina, once you old enough we can play games together!
      type: 3
    - quote: I would rather die then eat mums food...
      type: 3
    - quote: 'This stain on the wall looks kind of sus... '
      type: 3
    - quote: There is no god, only stupid man.
      type: 3
    - quote: I wonder if dad would die, if I put a spider in his sheets? Worth a
        try after he paid collage.
      type: 3
    - quote: 'I should pierce my bottom lip just to give granny a little heartattack
        here and now. '
      type: 3
    - quote: 'You call it family, I call it hetero-normative propaganda. '
      type: 3
    - quote: Gross, I have to bath in sanitizer now!
      type: 3
    - quote: 'Is that a rat?! Oh...just a shadow..right? '
      type: 3
    human: {fileID: 870211860256623442}
  - quotes:
    - quote: '*laughs* Hello little you!'
      type: 0
    - quote: ...ganma?
      type: 1
    - quote: 'Go away! *cries* '
      type: 2
    - quote: I love everything that's nice to me.
      type: 3
    - quote: 'The world is so yummy. '
      type: 3
    - quote: 'Look out, there could be monsters in the closet... '
      type: 3
    - quote: 'Mom locked away my clown costume because grandma didn''t liked it...but
        she said to keep it secret! '
      type: 3
    - quote: 'I want to play hide and seek, but only in teams! '
      type: 3
    - quote: Mommy hates scary movies. She says they're for stupid teenagers like
        Maxi.
      type: 3
    - quote: I'm gonna be the princess of mud when I'm big! But dad and grandma wouldn't
        visit me in my mud castle...How sad.
      type: 3
    - quote: Grandma has the best hugs!
      type: 3
    - quote: Grandma gives the best hugs!
      type: 3
    human: {fileID: 3575413651955645342}
  - quotes:
    - quote: 'Now look at that. I better clean it up before somone notices. '
      type: 0
    - quote: You don't treat an oldie like that
      type: 1
    - quote: 'Kreuzsackelzement & heilix Blechle!!! '
      type: 2
    - quote: My daughter is lucky she got a husband without any womenly skills to
        her.
      type: 3
    - quote: Maxi looks like a corpse already, how is he supposed to get a girl like
        this?
      type: 3
    - quote: There's an explanation for everything Pina, don't you worry.
      type: 3
    - quote: Let me clean that up, before somone notices.
      type: 3
    - quote: The only two things a woman has to fear is dieing alone and smelling
        like poop.
      type: 3
    - quote: Gosh, some day my little Pina will die by eating rat poisening or drinking
        gasoline.
      type: 3
    - quote: When Keira was still young she was a lot like her daughter. Heads always
        in cotton-candy clouds...
      type: 3
    - quote: Who took care of this place? Its so dusty everywhere...
      type: 3
    human: {fileID: 5696315045279839597}
